name: Toyota Corolla
description: The Toyota Corolla is a popular compact car known for its reliability, fuel efficiency, and comfortable ride. It is a perfect choice for daily commuting and family trips.

name: Ford Mustang
description: The Ford Mustang is an iconic American muscle car with a powerful engine and sleek design. It offers a thrilling driving experience and turns heads wherever it goes.

name: BMW 3 Series
description: The BMW 3 Series is a luxury sedan that combines performance, elegance, and advanced technology. It delivers a smooth ride and luxurious interior, making it a top choice among car enthusiasts.

name: Mercedes-Benz E-Class
description: The Mercedes-Benz E-Class is a sophisticated executive sedan with cutting-edge technology and opulent features. It offers a comfortable and refined driving experience, making it a symbol of luxury and prestige.

name: Tesla Model S
description: The Tesla Model S is an all-electric luxury sedan known for its impressive acceleration, long-range capabilities, and autonomous driving features. It is at the forefront of electric vehicle technology.

name: Honda Civic
description: The Honda Civic is a reliable and fuel-efficient compact car. It offers a comfortable interior, practical features, and excellent resale value. It's a favorite choice among budget-conscious buyers.

name: Audi A4
description: The Audi A4 is a premium compact sedan that combines performance, luxury, and advanced technology. It boasts a stylish design, powerful engine options, and a high-quality interior.

name: Chevrolet Silverado
description: The Chevrolet Silverado is a reliable and versatile pickup truck known for its towing capacity and cargo space. It is a popular choice among truck enthusiasts and business owners.

name: Subaru Outback
description: The Subaru Outback is a rugged and capable SUV with all-wheel drive and generous ground clearance. It is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and those who enjoy off-road adventures.

name: Nissan Rogue
description: The Nissan Rogue is a compact SUV that offers a comfortable ride, spacious interior, and advanced safety features. It is a family-friendly SUV with practical design and good fuel efficiency.

name: Jeep Wrangler
description: The Jeep Wrangler is an iconic off-road SUV known for its rugged capabilities and open-air driving experience. It is the perfect choice for adventure seekers and outdoor enthusiasts.

name: Hyundai Sonata
description: The Hyundai Sonata is a midsize sedan that offers a comfortable ride, user-friendly technology, and excellent fuel efficiency. It provides a smooth and reliable driving experience for daily commuting.
